<i>noun</i>: 불성실 [불썽실], 무성의 [무성의/무성이], 경박 [경박] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>불성실 [불썽실]</dt><br>
<dd>insincerity</dd><br>
<dd>태도나 행동이 진실하거나 정성스럽지 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>One's attitude or behavior being not truthful or sincere.</dd><br>
<dt>무성의 [무성의/무성이]</dt><br>
<dd>bad faith; insincerity</dd><br>
<dd>노력과 정성을 들이지 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>Lack of sincerity; the act of making no effort.</dd><br>
<dt>경박 [경박]</dt><br>
<dd>frivolity; flippancy; insincerity</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 조심스럽지 못하고 가벼움.</dd><br>
<dd>A lack of caution and gravity in words and or actions.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>